{"tid":2377530,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"各位佐敦居住員工 本 HR 決定酌情處理有關曠工事宜","createTime":"2021-01-23T16:21:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T17:01:19.000Z","uid":225931,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"680dc2e9064a9160f93bdca57de549cdd083f26f","tid":2377530,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根據香港勞工法例，曠工可以不須繳付代通知金，即炒，亦可扣薪及扣減勤工獎金，完全有法可依<br />\n<br />\n本來想炒咗你地，但應政府呼籲，本 HR 決定將曠工時數轉為將來 OT 時數，e.g. 今日曠工 24 小時，下個禮拜自願 OT 返 48 小時"},{"pid":"0d534ae2f121224988f9d17c4e9614001d50a1ac","tid":2377530,"uid":225931,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:23:33.000Z","msg":"Regards,<br />\n<br />\nHR team"},{"pid":"469816d5807b9601535f9fc41e1bd876756edb7e","tid":2377530,"uid":73611,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:26:21.000Z","msg":"追返呢兩人工<br />\n其他野唔追究就算啦<br />\n記得嘔返呢兩日人工出黎<br />\n如果唔係再同你計"},{"pid":"63e0ea4b96cc8dbc74de9382b3d8df0b4cfd2e4c","tid":2377530,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"469816d5807b9601535f9fc41e1bd876756edb7e","tid":2377530,"uid":73611,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:26:21.000Z","msg":"追返呢兩人工<br />\n其他野唔追究就算啦<br />\n記得嘔返呢兩日人工出黎<br />\n如果唔係再同你計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T17:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}